
## CLUTCH PEDAL INSPECTION  


## Clutch Pedal Height Inspection  


1. Measure the distance from the upper surface of the pedal pad to the cabin carpet.  


## Pedal height  


175- 180 mm {6.89- 7.09 in} (With carpet)  

![](images/0.jpg)
  


2. As necessary, adjust the height.  


## Clutch Pedal Free Play Inspection  


1. Depress the clutch pedal by hand until clutch resistance is felt.  


Free play 0.6- 3.1 mm {0.02- 0.12 in} Total free play 5- 13 mm {0.20- 0.51 in}  


2. Adjust the free play as necessary: (Refer to 05-10 CLUTCH PEDAL ADJUSTMENT, Clutch Pedal Free Play Adjustment.)